      "content": "okay i'll stick to the ibuprofen then. but i checked the cabinet and i don't have any kids syrup left. i have the regular aspirin though, i just don't want to give him too much. if i just crush up a small bit of an aspirin tablet, wouldn't that be fine for a kid his size? it's much faster than waiting for a pharmacy to open.",
